-- Romania Extends Offer Deadline for New Reactors, Mediafax Says
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2012-03-14T10:09:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-14/romania-extends-offer-deadline-for-new-reactors-mediafax-says.html
Romania  extended a deadline for
investor bids to build and operate two new nuclear reactors at
the Cernavoda plant near the  Black Sea  to Sept. 15 from March
15, news service  Mediafax  said today, citing Economy Minister
Lucian Bode.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  